<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can Beacon Hill School offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/42b4d7896de1c68b5ae3d7ccb499b14d.png" alt="ESF_Logomark_BW_RGB" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/marketing_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/43714c3649cc5c1736aaca151e47d03f.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong School-Family Connection</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We believe in fostering a strong partnership between schools and families. We actively encourage parental involvement and maintain open lines of communication to ensure that parents are fully engaged in their child's educational journey.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/parent_partnership/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/f516bccd5c38c9980ed9369cd977ee27.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Comprehensive Student Support</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our schools offer comprehensive support systems, including personalised guidance, pastoral care, and counselling services, to help students thrive academically, emotionally, and socially.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/98a0f52813fa5c3d87fa5c11b18c2c75.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Well-rounded Education</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Alongside academic excellence, our well-rounded education cultivates talents, interests, and character through diverse co-curricular activities in sports, arts, music, and community service.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/b76814538835b0739a48892213915752.png" alt="Real-world Experience" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Student Agency and Action</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Nurturing student agency and action empowers learners to take ownership, apply knowledge, and become agents of positive change in their communities.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/action_student_leadership/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/660cc3ca13253265900cfb7fb159a807.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Student Well-Being</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We foster students' social-emotional learning through assemblies, classroom integration, and cultivating respectful school relationships - empowering well-being and academic achievement.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/0b199e413913061f0aeadac3d10834d7.jpg" alt="beaconhill_2862" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Primary Years Programme (PYP)</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Years 1 - 6</button>
                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Beacon Hill School is an IB World School committed to educating open-minded seekers, supporting individual student needs, and developing the whole child's skills, attitudes, and global perspectives. The IB curriculum emphasises transdisciplinary learning, research, communication, and critical thinking to foster respect, responsibility, and meaningful action.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://beaconhill.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="section4" data-total="4">
