    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            const ori_total = parseInt($('#section4').data('total'));
            let slider_loop = ori_total >= 3 ? true : false;
            $('#section4').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: slider_loop,
                dummySlide: slider_loop,
				afterSlide: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
					if(slider_loop) {
						if(current_page == ori_total) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2).Slider('start');
						}
						if(current_page == ori_total * 2 + 1) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1).Slider('start');
						}
					}
				},
                afterInit: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
                    if(slider_loop) {
                        slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2);
                    }
                    else {
                        slider.Slider('jump', total_page);
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">Testimonials</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="tabs">
                                    <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Students</button>
                                    <button class="tab" data-id="2">Parents</button>
                                    <button class="tab" data-id="3">Alumni</button>
                            </div>
            <select class="tab-select" name="tab"><option value="1">Students</option><option value="2">Parents</option><option value="3">Alumni</option></select>                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                            <div class="record-slider">
                            <div class="slider-container">
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/6abbf0f06f65ed7f0597dc7153054936.jpg" alt="Student_Kaylee LUI" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>1 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I think BHS is an amazing school because they provide us with useful education. There is a nice balance between playtime and learning time. All the adults are nice to us and will always help us when we need help.<br>BHS makes me feel unique. Everyone is friendly and supportive and I feel it’s okay to be different, it’s okay to just be me.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">I think BHS is an amazing school because they provide us with useful education. There is a nice balance between playtime and learning time. All the adults are nice to us and will always help us when we need help.<br>BHS makes me feel unique. Everyone is friendly and supportive and I feel it’s okay to be different, it’s okay to just be me.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Kaylee Lui - Class of 2024</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/4bbffb862db49939b06a0d3820319747.jpg" alt="Student_Yoon Ah LEE" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>2 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Teachers are fun and understanding. They understand and support children’s feelings and will always try to make the best situation for everyone. BHS makes me feel safe because there are lots of people I can trust.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Teachers are fun and understanding. They understand and support children’s feelings and will always try to make the best situation for everyone. BHS makes me feel safe because there are lots of people I can trust.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Yoon Ah Lee - Class of 2026</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/3e371ddda201076283bea82d9b2dbc4c.jpg" alt="Student_Abby AU-YEUNG" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>3 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">BHS makes me happy. I like coming to school because I can sing and play with my friends. Teachers help me learn and I can learn lots of things like maths.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">BHS makes me happy. I like coming to school because I can sing and play with my friends. Teachers help me learn and I can learn lots of things like maths.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Abby Au-Yeung - Class of 2028</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content" data-id="2">
                                            <div class="record-slider">
                            <div class="slider-container">
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/e93d8dd99e904c49eab4acc8a9501e2c.jpg" alt="Parent_Paul" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>1 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">It has been two years since my three sons moved from a prestigious local school to be part of the Beacon Hill School family. I like what I have seen but I will stop short of saying it is the best decision; I would rather say this is a great educational program and an amazing environment to foster a positive learning attitude that would be helpful for their long-term development in this ever-changing world. My appreciation to the teachers for their continuous hard work, support and care!</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">It has been two years since my three sons moved from a prestigious local school to be part of the Beacon Hill School family. I like what I have seen but I will stop short of saying it is the best decision; I would rather say this is a great educational program and an amazing environment to foster a positive learning attitude that would be helpful for their long-term development in this ever-changing world. My appreciation to the teachers for their continuous hard work, support and care!</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Paul - Father of Jotham, Nathan, Ashton, Class of 2025 and 2027</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/0f623cf4faac8d628efeb228a261ce23.jpg" alt="Parent_Andrew" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
