                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Beacon Hill School has exceptional teachers, visionary leadership, and a strong sense of community. It has been a pleasure becoming part of this nurturing environment that fosters a love for learning.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
