                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">My son’s growth in BHS has been truly rewarding in terms of learning, culture, and being part of the global community. The transformation has been evident in the thought process, analytical thinking and problem-solving. His learning experience has been elevated by the wonderful team at BHS. Proud to be part of this community.</p>
