                        <h3>🏷: Student Achievement: Navya<br>.<br>📅: 7 March 2026<br>.<br>🖊: Navya participated in the Kowloon Cricket Club Match Play Series for 6–8-year-olds, where she emerged as the top player and won the gold medal.<br>Well done, Navya!<br>.<br>💬: #esfbeaconhillschool #beaconhillschoolhk #bhs #bhsig</h3>
