                                                    <h3>🏷: Student Achievement: Isabelle<br>.<br>📅: 10 March 2026<br>.<br>🖊: Isabelle took part in her Jazz exam and achieved Honours with Distinction. She loves Jazz dance and works very hard in her practice. Recently, she performed two dances at the AIA Carnival and had a great time.<br>Well done, Isabelle!<br>.<br>💬: #esfbeaconhillschool #beaconhillschoolhk #bhs #bhsig</h3>
