            <div class="lightbox" data-id="626">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>20/03/2026</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>🏷: Tag Rugby Club: HKPSSA Tag Rugby Championships<br>.<br>📅: 16 March 2025<br>.<br>🖊: It was an action-packed day of sport as both the Boys and Girls Tag Rugby teams competed in the HKPSSA Tag Rugby Championships. Both squads displayed excellent rugby and immense spirit throughout the tournament, and while we were unlucky that some results did not go our way, the quality of play was outstanding. The boys showcased strong attacking rugby and excellent support play, while the girls excelled in their passing and communication, scoring spectacular tries. A major highlight for the boys was successfully retaining the Lion Rock in their match against Shatin Junior, while the girls showed incredible grit by coming back from two tries down to draw against a strong Harrow team. Congratulations to Klaus and Tia, who were selected by their peers as the Most Valuable Players.<br>.<br>💬: #esfbeaconhillschool #beaconhillschoolhk #bhs #bhsig</h3>
